0.5.name: wordpress/hyperchecklist
0.5.description:
Create checklist and share those with specified users. You can assign a status to a list item:

  • Pending
  • Done
  • Error

You can have a checklist group for reuseing list items. This will help when you are creating list such as "pre release" or "things to do when i leave home" lists.

This plugin creates a page ("checklists") when you activates this plugin. You can change the name and slug if you want to.

To change css, just copy pluginfolder/css/lists.css to you template folder.
